For all designs I ask you to make, have them be beautiful, not cookie cutter. Make webpages that are fully featured and worthy for production.

By default, this template supports JSX syntax with Tailwind CSS classes, React hooks, and Lucide React for icons. Do not install other packages for UI themes, icons, etc unless absolutely necessary or I request them.

Use icons from lucide-react for logos.

All buttons in this project should follow these design principles:

Visual Style:

Use warm, vibrant colors (yellow/gold tones: #F5B800 or similar)
Rounded corners (typically rounded-lg or rounded-full for pill-shaped buttons)
Clean, modern aesthetic with good contrast
Text should be clearly legible with appropriate padding
Button Sizes:

Small Button: px-3 py-1.5, text-sm, icon size w-3 h-3
Medium Button (Standard): px-4 py-2, text-base, icon size w-4 h-4
Large Button: px-6 py-3, text-lg, icon size w-5 h-5
Extra Large Button: px-8 py-4, text-xl, icon size w-6 h-6
Minimum Dimensions:

Height: Minimum 40px (py-2.5) for touch-friendly interaction
Width: Auto-fit content with minimum px-4 padding
Icon spacing: mr-2 between icon and text
Button Variants:

Primary Button: Yellow/gold background (#F5B800), dark text, for main actions
Secondary Button: Outlined or lighter background, for secondary actions
Danger Button: Red tones for destructive actions
Disabled State: Reduced opacity (50-60%) and cursor-not-allowed
Typography:

Use medium or semibold font weight (font-medium or font-semibold)
Font size should be readable (text-sm to text-xl depending on size variant)
Text should have proper spacing and padding
Line height should be consistent (leading-normal or leading-tight)
Spacing & Sizing:

Padding horizontal: px-4 to px-8 depending on button size
Padding vertical: py-2 to py-4 depending on button size
Add icons using lucide-react when needed (positioned before text with mr-2 spacing)
Maintain consistent height across button types within same size category
Gap between multiple buttons: gap-2 or gap-3
Interaction States:

Hover: Slightly darker shade or subtle transform/shadow effect (hover:bg-[#E0A800])
Active: Pressed state with slight scale (active:scale-95) or color adjustment
Focus: Visible focus ring for accessibility (focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2)
Loading: Show spinner/loading state when processing, maintain button dimensions
Code Example Structure:


// Standard Medium Button (like "Gast hinzufügen")
<button className="bg-[#F5B800] hover:bg-[#E0A800] text-gray-900 font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition-all duration-200 flex items-center gap-2 min-h-[40px]">
  <Plus className="w-4 h-4" />
  Button Text
</button>

// Large Button
<button className="bg-[#F5B800] hover:bg-[#E0A800] text-gray-900 font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-all duration-200 flex items-center gap-2 text-lg min-h-[48px]">
  <Plus className="w-5 h-5" />
  Button Text
</button>

// Small Button
<button className="bg-[#F5B800] hover:bg-[#E0A800] text-gray-900 font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-all duration-200 flex items-center gap-2 text-sm min-h-[32px]">
  <Plus className="w-3 h-3" />
  Button Text
</button>
Responsive Sizing:

On mobile: Consider using full width (w-full) for primary actions
On tablet/desktop: Use auto width or max-width constraints
Adjust font size responsively: text-sm md:text-base lg:text-lg
Key Requirements:

Always use Tailwind CSS classes (no custom CSS files unless necessary)
Include transition effects for smooth interactions (transition-all duration-200)
Ensure buttons are responsive and work on mobile devices
Use semantic HTML (button element, not div)
Add appropriate aria-labels for accessibility when using icon-only buttons
Maintain minimum touch target size of 40x40px for mobile usability
Use flex items-center gap-2 for proper icon alignment
Dieser erweiterte Standard enthält nun präzise Größenangaben für alle Button-Varianten!

Modal Design Guidelines
All modals and popups in this project should follow these design principles:

Visual Style:

Dark blue gradient background (from dark navy to lighter blue tones)
Rounded corners on the modal container (rounded-xl or rounded-2xl)
White text for high contrast against dark background
Semi-transparent backdrop overlay behind modal
Clean, modern aesthetic with clear visual hierarchy
Modal Structure:

Header Section:

Icon on the left (yellow/gold background #F5B800, rounded-lg, with white icon)
Title text: Large, bold, white (text-xl or text-2xl, font-bold)
Subtitle text: Smaller, lighter gray/white (text-sm, text-gray-300)
Close button (X) on the top-right corner
Tab Navigation:

Horizontal tab bar below header
Active tab: Yellow/gold background (#F5B800), dark text, rounded-lg
Inactive tabs: Transparent/dark background, lighter text, rounded-lg
Icons before text labels (from lucide-react)
Tab sizes: px-4 py-2, text-sm, font-medium
Gap between tabs: gap-2
Content Section:

Dark blue background (slightly lighter than header)
Form fields with dark backgrounds and lighter borders
Labels: White text, text-sm, font-medium, with asterisk for required fields
Input fields: Dark background, light text, rounded-lg, border with subtle color
Full-width inputs for single-column layout
Two-column layout for related fields (E-Mail / Telefon)
Input Field Types:

Text inputs: Dark background, light border, white text, rounded-lg
Dropdowns/Selects: Same styling as text inputs with dropdown arrow
Button groups: Multiple buttons in a row with rounded corners and borders
Special selection buttons: Highlighted with blue background when selected
Footer Section:

Aligned to the right (flex justify-end)
Primary action button: Outlined style or yellow/gold background
Secondary action button: "Zurück" with subtle styling
Gap between buttons: gap-3
Sizing & Spacing:

Modal width: max-w-2xl to max-w-4xl depending on content
Padding: p-6 to p-8 for main content
Header padding: p-6 with border-bottom
Section spacing: space-y-4 to space-y-6
Input height: min-h-[44px] for accessibility
Form field spacing: gap-4 between fields
Color Palette:

Background gradient: from-[#0A1F3D] via-[#1a3a5c] to-[#2a4a6c]
Active elements: #F5B800 (yellow/gold)
Selected state: #3B82F6 (blue)
Text primary: white or text-gray-100
Text secondary: text-gray-300 or text-gray-400
Borders: border-gray-600 or border-gray-700
Toast/Notification System
Confirmation Messages:

After successful actions (save, delete, update, etc.), always show a toast notification with these characteristics:

Toast Types:

Success Toast:

Background: Green gradient (from-green-500 to-green-600)
Icon: CheckCircle or Check from lucide-react
Text: White, font-medium
Duration: 3-4 seconds
Error Toast:

Background: Red gradient (from-red-500 to-red-600)
Icon: XCircle or AlertCircle from lucide-react
Text: White, font-medium
Duration: 5-6 seconds
Warning Toast:

Background: Orange/amber gradient (from-amber-500 to-amber-600)
Icon: AlertTriangle from lucide-react
Text: White, font-medium
Duration: 4-5 seconds
Info Toast:

Background: Blue gradient (from-blue-500 to-blue-600)
Icon: Info from lucide-react
Text: White, font-medium
Duration: 3-4 seconds
Toast Positioning:

Default: Top-right corner (top-4 right-4)
Alternative: Top-center or bottom-center depending on context
Stack multiple toasts vertically with gap-2
Z-index: z-50 or higher to appear above modals
Toast Structure:

Width: min-w-[300px] max-w-[400px]
Padding: px-4 py-3
Rounded corners: rounded-lg
Shadow: shadow-lg for depth
Icon size: w-5 h-5
Close button: Optional X button on the right
Animation:

Entrance: Slide in from right with fade (translate-x-full to translate-x-0)
Exit: Slide out to right with fade (translate-x-0 to translate-x-full)
Duration: transition-all duration-300
Auto-dismiss: Fade out after specified duration
Code Example Structure:


// Modal with form
<div className="fixed inset-0 bg-black/50 flex items-center justify-center z-50">
  <div className="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0A1F3D] via-[#1a3a5c] to-[#2a4a6c] rounded-2xl max-w-3xl w-full mx-4 max-h-[90vh] overflow-hidden">
    {/* Header */}
    <div className="flex items-start gap-4 p-6 border-b border-gray-700">
      <div className="bg-[#F5B800] p-3 rounded-lg">
        <UserPlus className="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
      </div>
      <div className="flex-1">
        <h2 className="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Modal Title</h2>
        <p className="text-sm text-gray-300 mt-1">Subtitle text</p>
      </div>
      <button className="text-gray-400 hover:text-white">
        <X className="w-6 h-6" />
      </button>
    </div>

    {/* Tab Navigation */}
    <div className="flex gap-2 px-6 pt-4">
      <button className="bg-[#F5B800] text-gray-900 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg font-medium text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
        <User className="w-4 h-4" />
        Grunddaten
      </button>
      <button className="bg-transparent text-gray-300 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg font-medium text-sm flex items-center gap-2 hover:bg-gray-700/30">
        <Heart className="w-4 h-4" />
        Beziehung
      </button>
    </div>

    {/* Content */}
    <div className="p-6 space-y-4 overflow-y-auto">
      {/* Form fields */}
      <div>
        <label className="block text-sm font-medium text-white mb-2">
          Label<span className="text-red-400">*</span>
        </label>
        <input 
          type="text"
          className="w-full bg-[#1a3a5c] border border-gray-600 rounded-lg px-4 py-2.5 text-white placeholder-gray-400 focus:border-[#F5B800] focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#F5B800]/20 outline-none transition-all"
          placeholder="z.B. Maria Schmidt"
        />
      </div>

      {/* Two-column layout */}
      <div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div>
          <label className="block text-sm font-medium text-white mb-2">E-Mail</label>
          <input type="email" className="w-full bg-[#1a3a5c] border border-gray-600 rounded-lg px-4 py-2.5 text-white" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label className="block text-sm font-medium text-white mb-2">Telefon</label>
          <input type="tel" className="w-full bg-[#1a3a5c] border border-gray-600 rounded-lg px-4 py-2.5 text-white" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Footer */}
    <div className="flex justify-end gap-3 p-6 border-t border-gray-700">
      <button className="px-6 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-gray-300 border border-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-700/30 transition-all">
        Zurück
      </button>
      <button 
        onClick={handleSave}
        className="px-6 py-2.5 rounded-lg bg-[#F5B800] hover:bg-[#E0A800] text-gray-900 font-medium transition-all"
      >
        Speichern
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

// Success Toast Component
<div className="fixed top-4 right-4 z-50 animate-in slide-in-from-right duration-300">
  <div className="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-green-600 text-white px-4 py-3 rounded-lg shadow-lg flex items-center gap-3 min-w-[300px] max-w-[400px]">
